name: Pulp
description: Pulp is here for web3 organizations that want to get their word out about what they're doing. By leveraging time tested tooling, distribution channels and organic growth strategies we bring members to organizations to help them grow. By creating both marketing and community building initiatives, your organization will get its message out to the right people at the right time. Bring the power of The Market to your organization and grow your user base to the next level of engagement.
